</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">疗法</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">是指</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">重塑真实自我</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">，达到自我概念与经验的协调统一。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">行为</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">治疗</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">是</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">以减轻或改善患者的症状或不良行为为目标的一类心理治疗技术的总称。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">认知</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">疗法是根据人的认知过程，影响其情绪和行为的理论假设，通过认知和行为技术来改变患者的不良认知，从而矫正并适应不良行为的心理治疗方法</span></span></p><p><br/></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":40348,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-26 17:35:09","updateTime":"2019-06-26 17:35:09","isTrue":true,"questionId":9230,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">家庭治疗</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":40349,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-26 17:35:09","updateTime":"2019-06-26 17:35:09","isTrue":false,"questionId":9230,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">精神分析疗法</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":40350,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-26 17:35:09","updateTime":"2019-06-26 17:35:09","isTrue":false,"questionId":9230,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">人本主义疗法</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":40351,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-26 17:35:09","updateTime":"2019-06-26 17:35:09","isTrue"