"font-family:楷体\">行为。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">移情</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">是指在催眠疗法和自由联想法为主</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">体</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">的精神分析过程中，来访者对分析者产生的一种强烈的情感，是来访者将自己过去对生活中某些重要人物的情感投射到咨询者身上的过程。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">认同</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">是指个体向比自己</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">地位</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">或成就高的人的认同，以消除个体在现实生活中因无法获得成功或满足时，而产生的挫折所带来的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">焦虑。阻抗</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">是指咨询者在心理咨询过程中，以公开或隐蔽的方式否定咨询师的分析</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">拖延、对抗咨询师的要求，从而影响咨询的进展，甚至</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">使</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">咨询难以进行的一种现象。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">投射</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">是指个体依据其需要</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">、</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">情绪的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">主观</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">指向，将自己的特征转移到他人身上的现象。投射</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">作用</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">的实质是个体将自己身上所存在的心理行为特征推测成在他人身上也同样存在。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":40308,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-26 17:33:27","updateTime":"2019-06-26 17:33:27","isTrue":false,"questionId":9222,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">象征</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":40309,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-26 17:33:27","updateTime":"2019-06-26 17:33:27","isTrue":true,"questionId":9222,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">移情</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":40310,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-26 17:33:27","updateTime":"2019-06-26 17:33:27","isTrue":false,"questionId":9222,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">认同</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":40311,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-26 17:33:27","updateTime":"2019-06-26 17:33:27","isTrue":false,"questionId":9222,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">阻抗</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":40312,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-26 17:33:27","updateTime":"2019-06-26 17:33:27","isTrue":false,"questionId":9222,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">投射</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":1057,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 13:57:38","updateTime":"2019-06-09 13:57:38","name":"心理A2","questionCnt":10,"tagTypeId":49},{"id":1306,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 16:17:58","updateTime":"2019-06-09 16:17:58","name":"心理A2","questionCnt":10,"tagTypeId":55}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":9219,"createTime":"2019-06-26 17:32:37","topicId":null,"tagId":1057,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":7,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">女，</span>30 岁。因慢性皮肤溃疡迁延不愈需接受高压氧治疗。患者对高压氧舱的封闭环境感到十分恐惧。心理医生与患者进行了充分的沟通，在做好各种应急准备之后，让患者直接进入高压氧舱以快速克服恐惧心理。同时完成高压氧治疗。这种心理治疗方法是</span></p><p><br/></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"<p style=\"text-indent:16px\"><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">【答案解析】</span>①放松</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">训练是指是有机体从紧张状态松弛下来的一种练习过程</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">，目的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">是使</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">整个机体</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">活动水平降低，达到心理上的松弛，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">从而使</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">机体保持内环境平衡与稳定</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">；</span>②冲击疗法是</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">指通过直接</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">使</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">病人处于他所恐惧的情境之中，以受</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">物极必反</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">之效，从而消除恐惧</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">；</span>③厌恶</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">疗法又称</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">对抗性</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">发射疗法，是</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">采用</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">条件反射的方法把需要戒除的目标</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">行为</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">与不愉快的或者惩罚性的刺激结合起来，通过厌恶性条件反射，以消退目标行为对患者的吸引力，使症状消退。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">通常有</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">电击厌恶</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">疗</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">法、药物</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">厌恶疗</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">法、橡皮圈疗法、</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">想象</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">厌恶</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">疗</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">法</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">；</span>④系统脱敏的</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">基本原则是交互抑制，即当患者</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">面前</span></span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font